memakai jubah lima cakar?

336
00:27:02,799 --> 00:27:05,720
Biasanya adalah Keluarga Kekaisaran.

337
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,839
Dasar kain satin biru…

338
00:27:10,490 --> 00:27:11,920
