00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:42,880
Aku hanya mengingatkan.

346
00:27:43,039 --> 00:27:43,690
Mengingatkan?

347
00:27:45,119 --> 00:27:47,400
Saat Pejabat Kelas Tiga
melihat Raja datang,…

